=== Access ===
* About 15 minutes on foot from Meitetsu Nagoya Main Line {{ill|lt=Narumi Station|Q6966454|WD=Q6966454|1=Narumi Station}}
* About 1 minute on foot from Meitetsu Bus "Narumi Jinja" stop
* About 5 minutes on foot from Nagoya City Bus "Hanai" stop

